Hetu-adhipati
318.
653Hetu apacayagāmī dhammo hetussa apacayagāmissa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo…  tīṇi.
654Hetu apacayagāmī dhammo hetussa apacayagāmissa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo—  sahajātādhipati…  tīṇi.
655Nahetu apacayagāmī dhammo nahetussa apacayagāmissa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo—  sahajātādhipati…  tīṇi. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
319.
656Hetuyā tīṇi, adhipatiyā cha, sahajāte nava…pe…  upanissaye nava, kamme tīṇi, āhāre tīṇi, indriye nava, jhāne tīṇi, magge nava, sampayutte nava, atthiyā nava, avigate nava. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
